html: The Spirit of the Lord caused him to rest "The Spirit of Jehovah conducted them"— For תניחנו tenichennu , caused him to rest, the Septuagint have ὡδηγησεν αυτους , conducted them; they read תנחם tanchem . The Syriac, Chaldee, and Vulgate read תנחנו tanchennu , conducted him. Two MSS. have the word without the י yod in the middle.
